      "updated": 1713283200000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Firebase: system/intelligence/episodic/{tenant}/{skill}\nDecay: weight \u00d7 0.95^age_days. <0.3 \u2192 ready to\nconsolidate. >90d \u2192 archived. Retrievals bump count\n(frequent access stays relevant longer).",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Firebase: system/intelligence/episodic/{tenant}/{skill}\nDecay: weight \u00d7 0.95^age_days. <0.3 \u2192 ready to\nconsolidate. >90d \u2192 archived. Retrievals bump count\n(frequent access stays relevant longer).",
