      "locked": false,
      "text": "The A/B tester. Spawns candidate when avg error\n>0.15. Dual-scores every outcome against prod +\ncandidate weights. Promotes if 0.03+ better over\n20 obs + 14 days. Timing windows perturbed \u00b125%.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
