      "updated": 1713283200000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The patience engine.\nTracks: pending \u2192 24h \u2192 7d \u2192 closed\n(or expired after 14d). Firebase:\nsystem/intelligence/pending_outcomes/\n{client}/{prediction_id}. Channel-aware\nschedules (email 24/168h vs social 6/72h).",
