      "text": "The identifier finder. Knows 25 skills\nthat produce measurable outputs.\nRecursively extracts: campaign_id,\nsequence_id, ad_set_id, report_url.\nAttaches these to PendingOutcome so\nthe checkpoint processor knows where\nto look later.",
