    {
      "id": "ijpyueongmx1gm32",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 110,
      "y": 4150,
      "width": 3100,
      "height": 112,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#dee2e6",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 626285595,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1891776001,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1713283200000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\u2022 Firebase = internal working memory. Supabase = shared event bus across MH-OS, mh1-hq, mh1-skills, Jarvis.\n\u2022 API is synchronous & deterministic (sub-100ms memory lookups). Cron worker runs heavy consolidation every 5 min.\n\u2022 Memory decays exponentially \u2014 30-day episodes ~21% weight. Low-weight episodes are promoted to semantic patterns.\n\u2022 Semantic patterns update via Bayesian inference (Beta). Cross-skill patterns (3+ skills) become procedural wisdom.\n\u2022 Learning is weighted by signal quality. If marketer overrides everything, outcome teaches nothing.\n\u2022 Self-improvement never auto-deploys \u2014 every proposal goes through human review queue in Firebase.\n\u2022 Shadow A/B testing validates changes before promotion. Gold standard benchmarks prevent regression.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\u2022 Firebase = internal working memory. Supabase = shared event bus across MH-OS, mh1-hq, mh1-skills, Jarvis.\n\u2022 API is synchronous & deterministic (sub-100ms memory lookups). Cron worker runs heavy consolidation every 5 min.\n\u2022 Memory decays exponentially \u2014 30-day episodes ~21% weight. Low-weight episodes are promoted to semantic patterns.\n\u2022 Semantic patterns update via Bayesian inference (Beta). Cross-skill patterns (3+ skills) become procedural wisdom.\n\u2022 Learning is weighted by signal quality. If marketer overrides everything, outcome teaches nothing.\n\u2022 Self-improvement never auto-deploys \u2014 every proposal goes through human review queue in Firebase.\n\u2022 Shadow A/B testing validates changes before promotion. Gold standard benchmarks prevent regression.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
    }
  ],
